text: Ban Ban is a locality in the North Burnett Region, Queensland, Australia. In the , Ban Ban had a population of 34 people. ==Geography== The locality of Ban Ban completely surrounds the locality of Ban Ban Springs which is situated at the intersection of the Burnett Highway and Isis Highway. As such, both highways also cross Ban Ban as it surrounds the intersection. ==References== Category:Localities in Queensland Category:North Burnett Region
title: Ban Ban, Queensland
